ilder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" text_font_size=\"25px\" text_font=\"|600|||||||\" text_orientation=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]QUY TRÌNH CHẾ BIẾN[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" column_structure=\"1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/chon-nguyen-lieu.png\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_text=\"chon-nguyen-lieu\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" width=\"65%\" align=\"center\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_line_height=\"1.8em\" custom_padding=\"15px|14px|15px|14px|true|true\" background_color=\"rgba(224,58,49,0.91)\" border_radii=\"on|20px|20px|20px|20px\" header_4_font_size=\"17px\" header_4_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\"]<h4><strong>1. Chọn thịt bò</strong></h4>\n<p>Bò sạch, ăn cỏ thuần túy, Những con Bò đực lớn, trưởng thành. Phần thịt mông được chọn lọc kĩ lưỡng.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/tam-uop-gia-vi-cho-thit-bo.png\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_text=\"tam-uop-gia-vi-cho-thit-bo\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" width=\"65%\" align=\"center\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_line_height=\"1.8em\" custom_padding=\"15px|14px|15px|14px|true|true\" background_color=\"rgba(224,58,49,0.91)\" border_radii=\"on|20px|20px|20px|20px\" header_4_font_size=\"17px\" header_4_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\"]<h4><strong>2. Tẩm ướp gia vị</strong></h4>\nTừng miếng nhỏ ướp trong 5 giờ cùng các gia vị ướp thịt gia truyền, kèm các nguyên liệu chất lượng được chọn lọc.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/say-kho-thit-bo-1.png\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_text=\"say-kho-thit-bo-1\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" width=\"65%\" align=\"center\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_line_height=\"1.8em\" custom_padding=\"15px|14px|15px|14px|true|true\" background_color=\"rgba(224,58,49,0.91)\" border_radii=\"on|20px|20px|20px|20px\" header_4_font_size=\"17px\" header_4_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\"]<h4><strong>3. Cho vào lò sấy</strong></h4>\nThịt sau khi tẩm ướp cho vào lò sấy, thực hiện theo quy trình sản xuất thủ công 3-4 ngày mới được 1 mẻ.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/khach-hang-thuong-thuc.png\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_text=\"khach-hang-thuong-thuc\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" width=\"65%\" align=\"center\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_line_height=\"1.8em\" custom_padding=\"15px|14px|15px|14px|true|true\" background_color=\"rgba(224,58,49,0.91)\" border_radii=\"on|20px|20px|20px|20px\" header_4_font_size=\"17px\" header_4_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\"]<h4><strong>4. Phân phối sản phẩm</strong></h4>\nHong nguội thịt, chọn lọc lần cuối. Đóng gói kĩ, cách ly với môi trường bên ngoài trước khi tới tay người tiêu dùng.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f9f9f9\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" text_font_size=\"30px\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_font=\"Roboto||||||||\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" border_color_bottom=\"#E09900\"]BẢNG GIÁ KHÔ BÒ TRUYỀN THỐNG\n\n<hr style=\"max-width: 100px; height: 3px; ;background: red;\" />[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" text_font=\"Arial||on||||||\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_line_height=\"2em\" text_font_size=\"17px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]Bò khô (khô bò) đậm đà, được tẩm ướp gia vị đậm đà, cay mặn ngọt hoà quyện vào nhau. Bò khô được làm từ 100% thịt bò tươi nguyên chất, không phẩm màu, không chất phụ gia độc hại.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" column_structure=\"1_3,1_3,1_3\" background_enable_color=\"off\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_3\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" background_enable_color=\"off\" border_radii=\"on|30px|30px|30px|30px\" box_shadow_style=\"preset3\" box_shadow_vertical__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" box_shadow_vertical__hover=\"2px\" box_shadow_spread__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" box_shadow_spread__hover=\"0px\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" text_font=\"Arial||||||||\" text_font_size=\"16px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" background_color=\"#FFFFFF\" custom_padding=\"14px|50px|30px|50px|false|true\" text_line_height=\"2em\" header_3_text_color=\"#E02B20\" header_3_font_size=\"30px\" header_3_font=\"|600|||||||\"]<p>BÒ KHÔ 0,5 KG</p>\n<h3>360,000 đ</h3>\n<p>Bò khô nhà làm dạng miếng</p>\n<p>Quy cách: Đóng gói 0,5kg</p>\n<p>Trong túi hút chân không hoặc túi zíp</p>\n<p>Hạn dùng: 6 tháng</p>\n<p>Miễn phí vận chuyển cho đơn hàng từ 1 triệu</p>\n<p><a class=\"contact-home\" href=\"#\">ĐẶT MUA</a></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_3\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" background_enable_color=\"off\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_3\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', '