iv>\n</div>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" custom_padding=\"5px|10px|5px|10px|true|true\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<div class=\"check-ani\">\n<div class=\"img-check\"><img src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/check.png\" width=\"80\" height=\"268\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-68 alignnone size-full\" /></div>\n<div class=\"text-check\"><strong>Giao hàng toàn quốc</strong>\nVận chuyển miễn phí, giao hàng toàn quốc mọi giá trị đơn hàng.</div>\n</div>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_text_color=\"#000000\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" custom_padding=\"5px|10px|5px|10px|true|true\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<div class=\"check-ani\">\n<div class=\"img-check\"><img src=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/firewaller.png\" width=\"80\" height=\"267\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-67 alignnone size-full\" /></div>\n<div class=\"text-check\"><strong>Không chất bảo quản</strong>\nKhông sử dụng bất kỳ chất bảo quản nào. Chỉ sấy khô bằng lò.</div>\n</div>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#232323\" background_image=\"http://localhost/webkhobo/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Bo-kho-co-phuong-10-1.jpg\" parallax=\"on\" background_blend=\"overlay\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.17.4\" _module_preset=\"default\